title: Ceph Storage: Pools
agents: linux
catalog: os/storage
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the size and used space
 of pools of Ceph storage systems.

 The usage is checked against a warning and a critical level
 which can be specified in numerous ways.

item:
 The pool name.

discovery:
 One service is created for each pool.
